room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by The Puzzle Masters Escape Rooms in Tacoma
room_description: There are all sorts of rumors about Area 51. Our source says they have found and captured Aliens. One of the scientists experimenting on them has gone rogue and is trying to combine Alien DNA with Human DNA. The results are horrifying. Your mission is to Break Into Area 51 under the cover of night, recover the DNA and escape before you become the next experiment!
